Polymetal Slips for First Day in Five as Gold Price Retreats

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-08-15T15:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/polymetal-slips-for-first-day-in-five-as-gold-price-retreats-1-.html
OAO Polymetal, a Russian gold and
silver producer, declined for the first time in five sessions as
gold dropped.  The shares slid as much as 3.1 percent before closing down
0.2 percent at 565.50 rubles by 6:45 p.m. in Moscow.  Gold for December delivery fell $6.70, or 0.4 percent, to
$1,735.90 an ounce on the Comex in  New York .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran in Moscow at 
 jcorcoran13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
